{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"05f289bc3d","title":"关于土改准备工作致饶承石电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e3b36ff9ee","index":0,"year":1950,"month":1,"day":13,"articleId":"05f289bc3d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"0b46ab9868","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"05f289bc3d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"饶激石，当时任中共中央华东局第一书记、华东军政委员会主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8552ff7faa","type":"title","text":"关于士改准备工作致饶激石一电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"05f289bc3d"},{"id":"0b46ab9868","type":"paragraph","text":"绕淞石同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"05f289bc3d"},{"id":"692a17068c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一月九日报告收到，阅悉甚感。（二）土改准备工作中改造区乡政权极为重要，并须如期完成，否则不可能进行土改。（三）为要在今年冬季进行土改，必须在今年春夏秋三季完成土改的各项准备工作，时间颜紧，必须十分抓紧督促才能有成。（四）华东军政委员会似宜早日成立执行职务。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"05f289bc3d"},{"id":"f8b8d62ecf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"05f289bc3d"},{"id":"6e05c2adfb","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"05f289bc3d"}],"page":{"id":"e754406a81","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"05f289bc3d","start":165,"end":165}}}},"__N_SSG":true}